## Disqus

Disqus is a third part comments provider, which is very popular!

![disqus](http://cdn2.business2community.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/8-23-2012-11-42-11-AM.png)    

### Installation

- Register in [Disqus](http://disqus.com/) step by step
- Set your domain name, short name, e-mail, etc.
- Get the plungin code, insert it to your webpage template.

